rator\">&lt;</span>Button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>Click Here<span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Button<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Eso es todo!</p>\n<p>Ahora ve y dale una estrellita ðŸŒŸ en github ðŸ˜‰ðŸ‘‰<a href=\"https://github.com/lavaldi/normalized-components\">https://github.com/lavaldi/normalized-components</a></p>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"Hola amigos ðŸ‘‹ A continuaciÃ³n les presento un paquete de NPM que creÃ© para normalizar los diferentes elementos HTML y usarlos como styledâ€¦","frontmatter":{"title":"Normalized styled-components","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":150,"height":150,"src":"/static/d695fe69198cc4558284e9aec1a4892c/4148e/react.png","srcSet":"/static/d695fe69198cc4558284e9aec1a4892c/4148e/react.png 1x"}}},"banner":null,"slug":"normalized-styled-components","date":"2019-06-12T00:00:00.000Z","categories":["Code"],"tags":["react","styled-components","npm"],"template":"post"},"fields":{"slug":"/normalized-styled-components/","date":"2019-06-12T00:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/normalized-styled-components/"}}}